sense.gloss: to push into, to cram into, to stuff into, to crowd into
to break in, to burgle, to burglarize

sdata.j: ↑彼↑↓かれ↓は、まだスイッチを↑押↑↓|お↓し↑込↑↓こ↓む|↑力↑↓ちから↓を↑十分↑↓じゅうぶん↓↑持↑↓も↓ち↑合↑↓あ↓わせていた。
sdata.e: He was still strong enough to press a switch.

sdata.j: ただし↑押↑↓|お↓し↑込↑↓こ↓む|↑瞬間↑↓しゅんかん↓↑気圧↑↓きあつ↓の↑変化↑↓へんか↓のせいでしょうか、↑耳↑↓みみ↓がツンとするのが↑難点↑↓なんてん↓です。
sdata.e: However, maybe from the sudden change in pressure when you push them in, having your ears pop is a problem.
